title: United Kingdom 2 Year Note Yield
description: United Kingdom 2Y Bond Yield was 3.09 percent on Thursday November 3, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the United Kingdom 2 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 6.47 in June of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for UK 2Y.
